1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,680
Si alguna vez

2
00:00:00,680 --> 00:00:01,160
habéis visto

3
00:00:01,160 --> 00:00:02,480
un mueble perfecto

4
00:00:02,480 --> 00:00:04,280
tirado en la acera...

5
00:00:04,280 --> 00:00:04,920
y os habéis quedado

6
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:05,440
pensando

7
00:00:05,440 --> 00:00:05,840
qué pena,

8
00:00:05,840 --> 00:00:06,720
alguien lo querría.

9
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:07,160
Esto es

10
00:00:07,160 --> 00:00:08,360
para vosotros.

11
00:00:08,360 --> 00:00:08,920
Resulta que

12
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:10,000
cada vez más gente

13
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:10,640
en Valencia

14
00:00:10,640 --> 00:00:11,560
está haciendo algo

15
00:00:11,560 --> 00:00:12,720
al respecto.

16
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:14,400
Vecinos que ven cosas,

17
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:15,640
las fotografían,

18
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:16,880
y las comparten

19
00:00:16,880 --> 00:00:17,480
para que otro

20
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:18,280
las aproveche.

21
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:19,560
Y funciona.

22
00:00:19,560 --> 00:00:20,120
Os lo demuestro

23
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:20,760
ahora mismo.

24
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:21,400
Esta mesa negra

25
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:22,680
en Exposición

26
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:23,440
no iba a durar

27
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:24,240
mucho aquí.

28
00:00:24,240 --> 00:00:25,240
Mañana ya no estaría.

29
00:00:25,240 --> 00:00:26,200
Pero yo la he pillado

30
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:27,080
a tiempo.

31
00:00:27,080 --> 00:00:28,680
Va, que os lo cuento.

32
00:00:28,680 --> 00:00:29,800
La dejo en Givore.

33
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:30,400
Tardo menos

34
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:30,920
en subirla

35
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:32,120
que en explicároslo.

36
00:00:32,120 --> 00:00:32,960
Y lo que pasa después

37
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:34,240
es lo que me alucina:

38
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:35,200
gente que ni conozco

39
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:35,880
me escribe

40
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:36,880
para decirme

41
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:37,960
que la quiere.

42
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:38,920
Gente de este barrio,

43
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:39,680
de un par de calles

44
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:40,440
más allá.

45
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:41,240
Gente que ni sabía

46
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,240
que existía.

47
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:42,760
Y esa mesa

48
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:43,720
acaba en una casa.

49
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:44,600
No en un contenedor.

50
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:45,280
Esto lo creamos

51
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:45,760
entre todos.

52
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:46,680
Cada vez

53
00:00:46,680 --> 00:00:48,080
que alguien comparte,

54
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:49,120
la red crece.

